                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You took the falls badge. Told you - wings over shells. Remember it when the bugs get bigger."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The flock heard about the badge before I did. Birds gossip worse than my brother, and my brother is Ayo."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Kwame - after the badge",
                    Label: "badge_after"
                },
                {
