                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Heading for the Takehara gym? Free advice from a bird keeper - bug types fear the sky. Want the practical demonstration?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Every trainer walks this road staring at the flowers. Look up sometime. The answer to the first gym is circling right above you."
                        }
